text: Ravindrasinh Anirudhsinh Jadeja is an international cricketer from India. Ravindrasinh took part in the Indian Premier League as the captain of the Chennai Super Kings. He was born on December 6, 1988.Ravindra Jadeja == References == == Other websites == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers
